title: Bloomberg Markets: Chart of the Day, Eco Brief for Sept. 5

description:
Bloomberg Markets with Carol Massar and Cory Johnson. GUEST: Yelena Shulyatyeva Senior US Economist Bloomberg Intelligence Discussing the markets and economy with Bloomberg Stocks Editor Dave Wilson, who also discusses his Chart of the Day "S&P 500 total returns echo start of 1990s bubble years."
